m), for sprinkling"]}],"id":"r401708","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-M7R_05lVQTg\/XZQGHsEDe3I\/AAAAAAAAb6Y\/h_hyoUMNqKYQD5WZULGsnIZ-HuezsDSYACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_IZvcKLG5wLc-XMDJ.png","title":"Korean Fried Chicken","publishedAt":"2018-11-12T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"61 g","fat":"41 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"49 g","calories":"3427 kJ \/ 818 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl, deep fat fryer, paper towels, baking dish, cling film, refrigerator, oven","hintsAndTricks":["If a deep fat fryer is not available, heat oil in a deep saucepan, using a food thermometer to check the temperature reaches 190°C."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","3h 10m","4 portions"]}